The Abstract Factory Pattern

DESCRIPTION

There are two kinds of products: Product1 and Product2. CN and US make them differently.
Defines two seperate factories located in CN and US respectively.
The Client chooses different factories to make different products.

BUILD & RUN

	g++ Client.cpp
	./a.out

PROBLEMS

Who should be responsible for deleting the product?
	In this case it's the client. This makes the client code a little messy.
